# Team Guide

- Primary project doc fallback order starts with `AGENTS.md`.
- `TEAM_GUIDE.md` exists as an additional fallback file configured in `.codex/config.toml`.
- Keep README as ordinary content unless `project_doc_fallback_filenames` is changed.
- HTTP MCP auth should be derived from env bindings, not hard-coded secrets.
- The imported stdio server name is fixed to `filesystem`.
- The explicit HTTP server name is fixed to `tavily`.
